<br>
These drums have a 2.6 modifier to percussion instruments. This means that base song values are multiplied by 2.6 to create the final value when using these drums.<br>
<br>
They are also one of the most grossly overpriced pieces of bard equipment I have seen short of the White Dragon Scale.  People attempt to gouge Bards on these drums for prices of 30, 40, or higher than 50 thousand platinum.<br>
<br>
I want to sell these drums to a geniune Bard for 15k. They must be purchased in person by your Bard. I will not sell these to mules. I will not sell these to twinks. I request the Bard be over the level of 46 before attempting to purchase these. I sincerely hope that whichever Bard purchases them will not turn around and sell them for profit.<br>
<br>
